displaytitle: Study for Figure of Victory on Pectoral Brooch of Pallas Athena
medium: Pen and brown ink on light tan laid paper prepared with salmon wash
creditline: Gift of Peter W. Josten in memory of Stephen Spector
inscribed:
Inscribed recto, lower center, in brown ink:
ATENE; lower right center on gray inlaid border,
in brown ink (in Mariette hand): T.S.V. Plait; lower
left on blue decorative mat, lower left of gold
border, in black ink: 282; bottom center of blue
decorative mat, cartouche in black ink with brush
and blue wash: FR. PARMIGIANINO /1504–1540
